Short : Installer for Citadel 1.3 "Remonstered" edition
Type : Game
Author : Asman, Kane, Bored Seal, Psygore, Jean-Francois Fabre, Wepl

REQUIREMENTS:
The game requires 0.5 MB Chip Mem + 1 MB of other memory (fast RAM is used if possible).
Slave needs ROM image "DEVS:Kickstarts/kick34005.A500".
You need an additional 4.5 MB of memory for the preload option.

SUPPORTED VERSION:
- English version 1.3 only, bundled with the install

FEATURES:
- Significantly improved performance (4-5x +)
- Significantly updated in-game graphics
- Redesigned levels
- Rebalanced gameplay
- Extended backstory
- Modern WASD + mouse control
- Crosshairs 
- Removed "disturbances" and energy drain when hitting walls
- FPS (Frames per Second) display (press ` key)
- Auto-weapon change
- F1-F8 and numeric keys swapped for screen and weapon selection
- Fast weapon change (press R/T keys)
- Red hit and green take flash indications
- LMB support for skipping loading screens and intro
- Code protection fully removed
- New manual
- Unlimited Energy option built into the Install
- Fixed running on accelerators (see notes below)
- Improved exit option (double press ESC)
- Improved support for MC68040/60 based accelerators
- New icon
- Known bugs removed
- ... several other small improvements

HISTORY:
V1.0 (25-May-2001) - first release
V1.1 (17-Oct-2002) - poland version support added
V1.2 (08-Nov-2012) - fixed to work with WHDLoad v17+
V1.3 (03-Mar-2022) - "Remonstered" update (support for all other versions removed)

CHEAT CODES:
- Seriously?

BUGS:
- None :-)

NOTES:
- On some accelerators, especially those MC68040/60 based, the following 
  options may need to be added to whdload for the game to run smoothly as
  not all caches might be initialised by default:
   branchcache=0 cache=1 dcache=1
- Savegames are stored on Disk.4 file. You need to exit through the game (F10) 
  to flush the change to the HD (or set whdload options to flush while running)


         Bug report form, full WHDLoad package and other installs:
                           http://www.whdload.de
